<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Additional features not specified by GLSL specification. </para>

<para>EXT extensions are fully tested and documented.</para>

<para>Even if it&apos;s highly unrecommended, it&apos;s possible to include all the extensions at once by including &lt;glm/ext.hpp&gt;. Otherwise, each extension needs to be included a specific file. </para>
</section>
